{
  "video_id": "AFRmGkdXkxA",
  "title": "Stefan Larsson: What doctors can learn from each other",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12533.0,
      "end_time": 15880.0,
      "text": "Five years ago, I was on a sabbatical,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15890.0,
      "end_time": 17481.0,
      "text": "and I returned to the medical university"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17481.0,
      "end_time": 19343.0,
      "text": "where I studied."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19343.0,
      "end_time": 24980.0,
      "text": "I saw real patients and I wore the white coat"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24980.0,
      "end_time": 26907.0,
      "text": "for the first time in 17 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26907.0,
      "end_time": 30384.0,
      "text": "in fact since I became a management consultant."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30384.0,
      "end_time": 32308.0,
      "text": "There were two things that surprised me"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32308.0,
      "end_time": 34425.0,
      "text": "during the month I spent."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34425.0,
      "end_time": 36315.0,
      "text": "The first one was that the common theme"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36315.0,
      "end_time": 39823.0,
      "text": "of the discussions we had were hospital budgets"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 39823.0,
      "end_time": 41746.0,
      "text": "and cost-cutting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 41746.0,
      "end_time": 43570.0,
      "text": "and the second thing, which really bothered me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 43570.0,
      "end_time": 46439.0,
      "text": "actually, was that several of the colleagues I met,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 46439.0,
      "end_time": 48500.0,
      "text": "former friends from medical school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 48500.0,
      "end_time": 50637.0,
      "text": "who I knew to be some of the smartest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 50637.0,
      "end_time": 53606.0,
      "text": "most motivated, engaged and passionate people"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 53606.0,
      "end_time": 55160.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d ever met,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 55160.0,
      "end_time": 59900.0,
      "text": "many of them had turned cynical, disengaged,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 59910.0,
      "end_time": 62598.0,
      "text": "or had distanced themselves from hospital management."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 62598.0,
      "end_time": 65372.0,
      "text": "So with this focus on cost-cutting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 65372.0,
      "end_time": 69668.0,
      "text": "I asked myself, are we forgetting the patient?"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 69668.0,
      "end_time": 71672.0,
      "text": "Many countries that you represent"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 71672.0,
      "end_time": 73268.0,
      "text": "and where I come from"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 73269.0,
      "end_time": 76175.0,
      "text": "struggle with the cost of healthcare."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 76175.0,
      "end_time": 79143.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a big part of the national budgets."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 79143.0,
      "end_time": 82928.0,
      "text": "And many different reforms aim at holding back this growth."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 82928.0,
      "end_time": 84945.0,
      "text": "In some countries, we have long waiting times"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 84945.0,
      "end_time": 87151.0,
      "text": "for patients for surgery."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 87152.0,
      "end_time": 89670.0,
      "text": "In other countries, new drugs are not being reimbursed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 89670.0,
      "end_time": 92642.0,
      "text": "and therefore don&#39;t reach patients."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 92642.0,
      "end_time": 94899.0,
      "text": "In several countries, doctors and nurses"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 94899.0,
      "end_time": 98956.0,
      "text": "are the targets, to some extent, for the governments."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 98956.0,
      "end_time": 102523.0,
      "text": "After all, the costly decisions in health care"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 102523.0,
      "end_time": 104991.0,
      "text": "are taken by doctors and nurses."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 104991.0,
      "end_time": 107531.0,
      "text": "You choose an expensive lab test,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 107531.0,
      "end_time": 111158.0,
      "text": "you choose to operate on an old and frail patient."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 111158.0,
      "end_time": 115632.0,
      "text": "So, by limiting the degrees of freedom of physicians,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 115632.0,
      "end_time": 118863.0,
      "text": "this is a way to hold costs down."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 118863.0,
      "end_time": 121135.0,
      "text": "And ultimately, some physicians will say today"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 121135.0,
      "end_time": 123802.0,
      "text": "that they don&#39;t have the full liberty"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 123802.0,
      "end_time": 127322.0,
      "text": "to make the choices they think are right for their patients."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 127322.0,
      "end_time": 129692.0,
      "text": "So no wonder that some of my old colleagues"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 129692.0,
      "end_time": 132580.0,
      "text": "are frustrated."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 132580.0,
      "end_time": 134509.0,
      "text": "At BCG, we looked at this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 134509.0,
      "end_time": 136339.0,
      "text": "and we asked ourselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 136340.0,
      "end_time": 139852.0,
      "text": "this can&#39;t be the right way of managing healthcare."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 139852.0,
      "end_time": 143720.0,
      "text": "And so we took a step back and we said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 143720.0,
      "end_time": 145744.0,
      "text": "\"What is it that we are trying to achieve?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 145744.0,
      "end_time": 147975.0,
      "text": "Ultimately, in the healthcare system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 147975.0,
      "end_time": 151936.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re aiming at improving health for the patients,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 151936.0,
      "end_time": 154213.0,
      "text": "and we need to do so at a limited,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 154213.0,
      "end_time": 156700.0,
      "text": "or affordable, cost."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 156700.0,
      "end_time": 158793.0,
      "text": "We call this value-based healthcare."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 158793.0,
      "end_time": 160477.0,
      "text": "On the screen behind me, you see what we mean"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 160477.0,
      "end_time": 162286.0,
      "text": "by value:"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 162286.0,
      "end_time": 164772.0,
      "text": "outcomes that matter to patients"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 164772.0,
      "end_time": 167780.0,
      "text": "relative to the money we spend."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 167781.0,
      "end_time": 170526.0,
      "text": "This was described beautifully in a book in 2006"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 170526.0,
      "end_time": 174531.0,
      "text": "by Michael Porter and Elizabeth Teisberg."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 174531.0,
      "end_time": 177674.0,
      "text": "On this picture, you have my father-in-law"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 177674.0,
      "end_time": 181600.0,
      "text": "surrounded by his three beautiful daughters."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 181600.0,
      "end_time": 184960.0,
      "text": "When we started doing our research at BCG,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 184960.0,
      "end_time": 186756.0,
      "text": "we decided not to look so much at the costs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 186756.0,
      "end_time": 189296.0,
      "text": "but to look at the quality instead,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 189296.0,
      "end_time": 191876.0,
      "text": "and in the research, one of the things"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 191877.0,
      "end_time": 194919.0,
      "text": "that fascinated us was the variation we saw."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 194919.0,
      "end_time": 197292.0,
      "text": "You compare hospitals in a country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 197292.0,
      "end_time": 199508.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ll find some that are extremely good,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 199508.0,
      "end_time": 202953.0,
      "text": "but you&#39;ll find a large number that are vastly much worse."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 202953.0,
      "end_time": 205115.0,
      "text": "The differences were dramatic."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 205115.0,
      "end_time": 207177.0,
      "text": "Erik, my father-in-law,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 207177.0,
      "end_time": 209708.0,
      "text": "he suffers from prostate cancer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 209708.0,
      "end_time": 212180.0,
      "text": "and he probably needs surgery."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 212180.0,
      "end_time": 214725.0,
      "text": "Now living in Europe, he can choose to go to Germany"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 214725.0,
      "end_time": 218436.0,
      "text": "that has a well-reputed healthcare system."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 218437.0,
      "end_time": 222137.0,
      "text": "If he goes there and goes to the average hospital,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 222137.0,
      "end_time": 226211.0,
      "text": "he will have the risk of becoming incontinent"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 226211.0,
      "end_time": 228185.0,
      "text": "by about 50 percent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 228185.0,
      "end_time": 231158.0,
      "text": "so he would have to start wearing diapers again."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 231158.0,
      "end_time": 235950.0,
      "text": "You flip a coin. Fifty percent risk. That&#39;s quite a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 235950.0,
      "end_time": 237997.0,
      "text": "If he instead would go to Hamburg,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 237997.0,
      "end_time": 240508.0,
      "text": "and to a clinic called the Martini-Klinik,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 240508.0,
      "end_time": 243191.0,
      "text": "the risk would be only one in 20."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 243191.0,
      "end_time": 244776.0,
      "text": "Either you a flip a coin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 244776.0,
      "end_time": 246809.0,
      "text": "or you have a one in 20 risk."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 246809.0,
      "end_time": 250314.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s a huge difference, a seven-fold difference."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 250314.0,
      "end_time": 252299.0,
      "text": "When we look at many hospitals"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 252299.0,
      "end_time": 253973.0,
      "text": "for many different diseases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 253973.0,
      "end_time": 256990.0,
      "text": "we see these huge differences."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 256990.0,
      "end_time": 259884.0,
      "text": "But you and I don&#39;t know. We don&#39;t have the data."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 259884.0,
      "end_time": 261731.0,
      "text": "And often, the data actually doesn&#39;t exist."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 261731.0,
      "end_time": 263450.0,
      "text": "Nobody knows."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 263450.0,
      "end_time": 267803.0,
      "text": "So going the hospital is a lottery."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 267803.0,
      "end_time": 272820.0,
      "text": "Now, it doesn&#39;t have to be that way. There is hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 272830.0,
      "end_time": 274575.0,
      "text": "In the late &#39;70s, there were a group"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 274575.0,
      "end_time": 277700.0,
      "text": "of Swedish orthopedic surgeons"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 277700.0,
      "end_time": 278866.0,
      "text": "who met at their annual meeting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 278866.0,
      "end_time": 280827.0,
      "text": "and they were discussing the different procedures"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 280827.0,
      "end_time": 284131.0,
      "text": "they used to operate hip surgery."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 284131.0,
      "end_time": 285859.0,
      "text": "To the left of this slide, you see a variety"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 285859.0,
      "end_time": 288895.0,
      "text": "of metal pieces, artificial hips that you would use"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 288896.0,
      "end_time": 291755.0,
      "text": "for somebody who needs a new hip."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 291755.0,
      "end_time": 295400.0,
      "text": "They all realized they had their individual way of operating."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 295400.0,
      "end_time": 297401.0,
      "text": "They all argued that, \"My technique is the best,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 297401.0,
      "end_time": 300274.0,
      "text": "but none of them actually knew, and they admitted that."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 300274.0,
      "end_time": 304223.0,
      "text": "So they said, \"We probably need to measure quality"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 304223.0,
      "end_time": 308392.0,
      "text": "so we know and can learn from what&#39;s best.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 308392.0,
      "end_time": 311591.0,
      "text": "So they in fact spent two years debating,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 311591.0,
      "end_time": 313886.0,
      "text": "\"So what is quality in hip surgery?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 313886.0,
      "end_time": 316260.0,
      "text": "\"Oh, we should measure this.\" \"No, we should measure that.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 316260.0,
      "end_time": 318311.0,
      "text": "And they finally agreed."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 318311.0,
      "end_time": 320962.0,
      "text": "And once they had agreed, they started measuring,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 320962.0,
      "end_time": 323365.0,
      "text": "and started sharing the data."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 323365.0,
      "end_time": 325964.0,
      "text": "Very quickly, they found that if you put cement"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 325964.0,
      "end_time": 327469.0,
      "text": "in the bone of the patient"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 327470.0,
      "end_time": 329648.0,
      "text": "before you put the metal shaft in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 329648.0,
      "end_time": 331784.0,
      "text": "it actually lasted a lot longer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 331784.0,
      "end_time": 333542.0,
      "text": "and most patients would never have to be"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 333542.0,
      "end_time": 335902.0,
      "text": "re-operated on in their lifetime."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 335903.0,
      "end_time": 337571.0,
      "text": "They published the data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 337571.0,
      "end_time": 340694.0,
      "text": "and it actually transformed clinical practice in the country."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 340694.0,
      "end_time": 343985.0,
      "text": "Everybody saw this makes a lot of sense."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 343985.0,
      "end_time": 346220.0,
      "text": "Since then, they publish every year."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 346220.0,
      "end_time": 347969.0,
      "text": "Once a year, they publish the league table:"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 347970.0,
      "end_time": 350457.0,
      "text": "who&#39;s best, who&#39;s at the bottom?"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 350457.0,
      "end_time": 353137.0,
      "text": "And they visit each other to try to learn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 353137.0,
      "end_time": 356927.0,
      "text": "so a continuous cycle of improvement."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 356927.0,
      "end_time": 359734.0,
      "text": "For many years, Swedish hip surgeons"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 359734.0,
      "end_time": 362121.0,
      "text": "had the best results in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 362121.0,
      "end_time": 364599.0,
      "text": "at least for those who actually were measuring,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 364599.0,
      "end_time": 367340.0,
      "text": "and many were not."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 367350.0,
      "end_time": 369917.0,
      "text": "Now I found this principle really exciting."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 369917.0,
      "end_time": 371719.0,
      "text": "So the physicians get together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 371720.0,
      "end_time": 373845.0,
      "text": "they agree on what quality is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 373845.0,
      "end_time": 377559.0,
      "text": "they start measuring, they share the data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 377559.0,
      "end_time": 381750.0,
      "text": "they find who&#39;s best, and they learn from it."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 381750.0,
      "end_time": 383667.0,
      "text": "Continuous improvement."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 383667.0,
      "end_time": 386215.0,
      "text": "Now, that&#39;s not the only exciting part."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 386215.0,
      "end_time": 388465.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s exciting in itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 388466.0,
      "end_time": 391417.0,
      "text": "But if you bring back the cost side of the equation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 391417.0,
      "end_time": 392876.0,
      "text": "and look at that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 392877.0,
      "end_time": 395882.0,
      "text": "it turns out, those who have focused on quality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 395882.0,
      "end_time": 397915.0,
      "text": "they actually also have the lowest costs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 397915.0,
      "end_time": 400584.0,
      "text": "although that&#39;s not been the purpose in the first place."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 400584.0,
      "end_time": 403614.0,
      "text": "So if you look at the hip surgery story again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 403614.0,
      "end_time": 405984.0,
      "text": "there was a study done a couple years ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 405985.0,
      "end_time": 409983.0,
      "text": "where they compared the U.S. and Sweden."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 409983.0,
      "end_time": 411908.0,
      "text": "They looked at how many patients have needed"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 411908.0,
      "end_time": 415989.0,
      "text": "to be re-operated on seven years after the first surgery."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 415989.0,
      "end_time": 418876.0,
      "text": "In the United States, the number was three times"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 418876.0,
      "end_time": 421630.0,
      "text": "higher than in Sweden."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 421640.0,
      "end_time": 424504.0,
      "text": "So many unnecessary surgeries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 424504.0,
      "end_time": 427244.0,
      "text": "and so much unnecessary suffering"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 427244.0,
      "end_time": 428936.0,
      "text": "for all the patients who were operated on"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 428936.0,
      "end_time": 431402.0,
      "text": "in that seven year period."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 431403.0,
      "end_time": 432982.0,
      "text": "Now, you can imagine how much savings"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 432982.0,
      "end_time": 435482.0,
      "text": "there would be for society."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 435482.0,
      "end_time": 438653.0,
      "text": "We did a study where we looked at OECD data."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 438653.0,
      "end_time": 441503.0,
      "text": "OECD does, every so often,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 441503.0,
      "end_time": 443659.0,
      "text": "look at quality of care"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 443659.0,
      "end_time": 448183.0,
      "text": "where they can find the data across the member countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 448184.0,
      "end_time": 450786.0,
      "text": "The United States has, for many diseases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 450786.0,
      "end_time": 452990.0,
      "text": "actually a quality which is below the average"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 452990.0,
      "end_time": 454408.0,
      "text": "in OECD."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 454408.0,
      "end_time": 456562.0,
      "text": "Now, if the American healthcare system"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 456562.0,
      "end_time": 458998.0,
      "text": "would focus a lot more on measuring quality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 458998.0,
      "end_time": 463460.0,
      "text": "and raise quality just to the level of average OECD,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 463470.0,
      "end_time": 465385.0,
      "text": "it would save the American people"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 465385.0,
      "end_time": 469510.0,
      "text": "500 billion U.S. dollars a year."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 469511.0,
      "end_time": 472738.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s 20 percent of the budget,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 472738.0,
      "end_time": 475451.0,
      "text": "of the healthcare budget of the country."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 475451.0,
      "end_time": 477558.0,
      "text": "Now you may say that these numbers"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 477558.0,
      "end_time": 480449.0,
      "text": "are fantastic, and it&#39;s all logical,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 480449.0,
      "end_time": 482459.0,
      "text": "but is it possible?"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 482459.0,
      "end_time": 485980.0,
      "text": "This would be a paradigm shift in healthcare,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 485980.0,
      "end_time": 488678.0,
      "text": "and I would argue that not only can it be done,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 488678.0,
      "end_time": 490912.0,
      "text": "but it has to be done."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 490912.0,
      "end_time": 494303.0,
      "text": "The agents of change are the doctors and nurses"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 494303.0,
      "end_time": 496995.0,
      "text": "in the healthcare system."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 496995.0,
      "end_time": 499109.0,
      "text": "In my practice as a consultant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 499109.0,
      "end_time": 501376.0,
      "text": "I meet probably a hundred or more than a hundred"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 501376.0,
      "end_time": 504253.0,
      "text": "doctors and nurses and other hospital"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 504253.0,
      "end_time": 507210.0,
      "text": "or healthcare staff every year."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 507210.0,
      "end_time": 509395.0,
      "text": "The one thing they have in common is"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 509396.0,
      "end_time": 511674.0,
      "text": "they really care about what they achieve"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 511674.0,
      "end_time": 514908.0,
      "text": "in terms of quality for their patients."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 514908.0,
      "end_time": 516991.0,
      "text": "Physicians are, like most of you in the audience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 516991.0,
      "end_time": 519526.0,
      "text": "very competitive."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 519527.00000000006,
      "end_time": 521277.00000000006,
      "text": "They were always best in class."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 521277.00000000006,
      "end_time": 524775.0,
      "text": "We were always best in class."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 524775.0,
      "end_time": 527389.0,
      "text": "And if somebody can show them that the result"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 527389.0,
      "end_time": 528976.0,
      "text": "they perform for their patients"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 528976.0,
      "end_time": 531830.0,
      "text": "is no better than what others do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 531830.0,
      "end_time": 534537.0,
      "text": "they will do whatever it takes to improve."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 534537.0,
      "end_time": 536870.0,
      "text": "But most of them don&#39;t know."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 536870.0,
      "end_time": 539285.0,
      "text": "But physicians have another characteristic."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 539285.0,
      "end_time": 543127.0,
      "text": "They actually thrive from peer recognition."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 543127.0,
      "end_time": 545361.0,
      "text": "If a cardiologist calls another cardiologist"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 545361.0,
      "end_time": 547209.0,
      "text": "in a competing hospital"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 547209.0,
      "end_time": 549238.0,
      "text": "and discusses why that other hospital"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 549238.0,
      "end_time": 552330.0,
      "text": "has so much better results, they will share."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 552330.0,
      "end_time": 555750.0,
      "text": "They will share the information on how to improve."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 555750.0,
      "end_time": 559870.0,
      "text": "So it is, by measuring and creating transparency,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 559870.0,
      "end_time": 562780.0,
      "text": "you get a cycle of continuous improvement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 562780.0,
      "end_time": 565654.0,
      "text": "which is what this slide shows."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 565654.0,
      "end_time": 568595.0,
      "text": "Now, you may say this is a nice idea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 568595.0,
      "end_time": 570499.0,
      "text": "but this isn&#39;t only an idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 570499.0,
      "end_time": 572527.0,
      "text": "This is happening in reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 572527.0,
      "end_time": 575681.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re creating a global community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 575681.0,
      "end_time": 577544.0,
      "text": "and a large global community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 577544.0,
      "end_time": 580910.0,
      "text": "where we&#39;ll be able to measure and compare"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 580910.0,
      "end_time": 581805.0,
      "text": "what we achieve."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 581805.0,
      "end_time": 584431.0,
      "text": "Together with two academic institutions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 584432.0,
      "end_time": 586426.0,
      "text": "Michael Porter at Harvard Business School,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 586426.0,
      "end_time": 588310.0,
      "text": "and the Karolinska Institute in Sweden,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 588310.0,
      "end_time": 592275.0,
      "text": "BCG has formed something we call ICHOM."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 592275.0,
      "end_time": 594480.0,
      "text": "You may think that&#39;s a sneeze,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 594480.0,
      "end_time": 597607.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s not a sneeze, it&#39;s an acronym."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 597607.0,
      "end_time": 600183.0,
      "text": "It stands for the International Consortium"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 600183.0,
      "end_time": 603143.0,
      "text": "for Health Outcome Measurement."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 603143.0,
      "end_time": 605892.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re bringing together leading physicians"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 605892.0,
      "end_time": 609483.0,
      "text": "and patients to discuss, disease by disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 609483.0,
      "end_time": 611584.0,
      "text": "what is really quality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 611585.0,
      "end_time": 613572.0,
      "text": "what should we measure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 613572.0,
      "end_time": 616600.0,
      "text": "and to make those standards global."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 616600.0,
      "end_time": 618415.0,
      "text": "They&#39;ve worked -- four working groups have worked"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 618415.0,
      "end_time": 620382.0,
      "text": "during the past year:"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 620383.0,
      "end_time": 623227.0,
      "text": "cataracts, back pain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 623227.0,
      "end_time": 627453.0,
      "text": "coronary artery disease, which is, for instance, heart attack,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 627453.0,
      "end_time": 629634.0,
      "text": "and prostate cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 629634.0,
      "end_time": 632380.0,
      "text": "The four groups will publish their data"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 632380.0,
      "end_time": 633880.0,
      "text": "in November of this year."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 633880.0,
      "end_time": 636338.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the first time we&#39;ll be comparing"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 636338.0,
      "end_time": 639284.0,
      "text": "apples to apples, not only within a country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 639284.0,
      "end_time": 642465.0,
      "text": "but between countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 642465.0,
      "end_time": 646443.0,
      "text": "Next year, we&#39;re planning to do eight diseases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 646443.0,
      "end_time": 648997.0,
      "text": "the year after, 16."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 648997.0,
      "end_time": 651453.0,
      "text": "In three years&#39; time, we plan to have covered"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 651453.0,
      "end_time": 654566.0,
      "text": "40 percent of the disease burden."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 654566.0,
      "end_time": 657216.0,
      "text": "Compare apples to apples. Who&#39;s better?"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 657216.0,
      "end_time": 660267.0,
      "text": "Why is that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 660267.0,
      "end_time": 663132.0,
      "text": "Five months ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 663132.0,
      "end_time": 666165.0,
      "text": "I led a workshop at the largest university hospital"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 666166.0,
      "end_time": 667876.0,
      "text": "in Northern Europe."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 667876.0,
      "end_time": 671363.0,
      "text": "They have a new CEO, and she has a vision:"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 671363.0,
      "end_time": 674969.0,
      "text": "I want to manage my big institution much more"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 674969.0,
      "end_time": 679740.0,
      "text": "on quality, outcomes that matter to patients."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 679740.0,
      "end_time": 682572.0,
      "text": "This particular day, we sat in a workshop"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 682572.0,
      "end_time": 685382.0,
      "text": "together with physicians, nurses and other staff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 685382.0,
      "end_time": 689880.0,
      "text": "discussing leukemia in children."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 689880.0,
      "end_time": 691657.0,
      "text": "The group discussed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 691657.0,
      "end_time": 693697.0,
      "text": "how do we measure quality today?"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 693697.0,
      "end_time": 696262.0,
      "text": "Can we measure it better than we do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 696262.0,
      "end_time": 698483.0,
      "text": "We discussed, how do we treat these kids,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 698484.0,
      "end_time": 700535.0,
      "text": "what are important improvements?"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 700535.0,
      "end_time": 703315.0,
      "text": "And we discussed what are the costs for these patients,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 703316.0,
      "end_time": 705664.0,
      "text": "can we do treatment more efficiently?"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 705664.0,
      "end_time": 707608.0,
      "text": "There was an enormous energy in the room."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 707608.0,
      "end_time": 711970.0,
      "text": "There were so many ideas, so much enthusiasm."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 711970.0,
      "end_time": 713391.0,
      "text": "At the end of the meeting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 713391.0,
      "end_time": 716699.0,
      "text": "the chairman of the department, he stood up."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 716700.0,
      "end_time": 721277.0,
      "text": "He looked over the group and he said --"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 721277.0,
      "end_time": 723620.0,
      "text": "first he raised his hand, I forgot that --"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 723620.0,
      "end_time": 725531.0,
      "text": "he raised his hand, clenched his fist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 725531.0,
      "end_time": 728428.0,
      "text": "and then he said to the group, \"Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 728428.0,
      "end_time": 731351.0,
      "text": "Thank you. Today, we&#39;re finally discussing"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 731351.0,
      "end_time": 734925.0,
      "text": "what this hospital does the right way.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 734925.0,
      "end_time": 737120.0,
      "text": "By measuring value in healthcare,"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 737120.0,
      "end_time": 739360.0,
      "text": "that is not only costs"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 739370.0,
      "end_time": 741510.0,
      "text": "but outcomes that matter to patients,"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 741510.0,
      "end_time": 743308.0,
      "text": "we will make staff in hospitals"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 743308.0,
      "end_time": 745167.0,
      "text": "and elsewhere in the healthcare system"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 745167.0,
      "end_time": 749261.0,
      "text": "not a problem but an important part of the solution."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 749261.0,
      "end_time": 751197.0,
      "text": "I believe measuring value in healthcare"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 751197.0,
      "end_time": 753968.0,
      "text": "will bring about a revolution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 753968.0,
      "end_time": 756770.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m convinced that the founder"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 756770.0,
      "end_time": 759540.0,
      "text": "of modern medicine, the Greek Hippocrates,"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 759540.0,
      "end_time": 762490.0,
      "text": "who always put the patient at the center,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
